ref=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Notation.html#Bot.bot\">⊥</a> →\n        <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">g₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">g₂</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Spec\">Spec</a> <span class=\"fn\">R</span></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">X</span>),\n          <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Spec.map\">Spec.map</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">g₁</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Spec.map\">Spec.map</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">g₂</span></span> →\n            <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">g₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">g₂</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\">g₁</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">g₂</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/FormallyUnramified.html#AlgebraicGeometry.FormallyUnramified\">FormallyUnramified</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"To show that `f : X ⟶ Y` is formally unramified,\nit suffices to check for that every following commuting diagram\n```\nSpec R --→ X\n  |        |\n  ↓        ↓\nSpec S --→ Y\n```\nwith `S = R/I` for some `I² = 0`, there exists at most one arrow `Spec S ⟶ X` making\nthe diagram commute.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/FormallyUnramified.html#AlgebraicGeometry.FormallyUnramified.of_hom_ext","kind":"theorem","line":227,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.FormallyUnramified.of_hom_ext","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/FormallyUnramified.lean#L227-L257"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/FormallyUnramified.html#AlgebraicGeometry.FormallyUnramified.hom_ext\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">FormallyUnramified</span>.<span class=\"name\">hom_ext</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">X </span><span class=\"fn\">Y </span><span class=\"fn\">Z' </span><span class=\"fn\">Z</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme\">Scheme</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Z'</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">Z</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hi</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/GroupWithZero/Basic.html#IsNilpotent\">IsNilpotent</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/IdealSheaf/Basic.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Hom.ker\">Scheme.Hom.ker</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/ClosedImmersion.html#AlgebraicGeometry.IsClosedImmersion\">IsClosedImmersion</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\">X</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">Y</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Morphisms/FormallyUnramified.html#AlgebraicGeometry.FormallyUnramified\">FormallyUnramified</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">g₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">g₂</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Z</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\">X</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hig</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">g₁</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">g₂</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hgf</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp\">CategoryTheory.CategoryStruct.comp</a> <span class=\"fn\">g₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span> <a href=\"